#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:5
msgid "策略思路"
msgstr "Strategy and Ideas"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:7
msgid "原始思路为“滑窗特征 + SVM 二分类”；"
msgstr ""
"The original idea was \"sliding window features + SVM binary "
"classification\";"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:8
msgid ""
"教学骨架版强调 qteasy 的链路：`特征/预测` -> `信号` -> `回测`；"
msgstr ""
"The teaching framework emphasizes the Qteasy workflow: `feature/"
"prediction` -> `signal` -> `backtesting`;"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:9
msgid ""
"默认实现不在回测循环中重复重训练，而是用轻量规则近似模型输出，避免性"
"能和可复现问题。"
msgstr ""
"The default implementation avoids repeated retraining in the "
"backtesting loop, instead approximating the model output with "
"lightweight rules to avoid performance and reproducibility issues."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:11
msgid "诚实说明"
msgstr "Honesty"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:13
msgid ""
"若要使用真实机器学习模型，建议在策略外离线训练并固化预测结果，再在策"
"略中读取；"
msgstr ""
"If you want to use a real machine learning model, it is recommended "
"to train it offline outside the policy and solidify the prediction "
"results before reading them into the policy."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:14
msgid "这样更容易避免前视偏差，并控制优化模式的运行成本。"
msgstr ""
"This makes it easier to avoid forward bias and control the "
"operating costs of the optimization mode."

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:39
msgid "可执行脚本"
msgstr "Executable script"

#: ../../source/examples/Example_14_机器学习选股.md:41
msgid "`examples/strategy_example_14.py`"
msgstr "`examples/strategy_example_14.py`"
